  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/xbox-one-hardware-problem-free-game/\"><img alt=\"Microsoft giving a free game to owners of Xbox Ones with hardware problems\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/e1da8f09b5aedadeeda7683a4cc77bad/xboxone_console_leadimg_630px.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说微软已经卖出了<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/23/xbox-one-crosses-million-sold-mark-in-under-24-hours/\">一大堆</a> <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/xboxone\">Xbox One</a>，但在首批入手的玩家中，却有一些遭遇到了硬件危机。问题主要都集中在光碟机上，有的机器是塞入光碟后只进不出，有的是弹出光碟时会有奇怪的声响。对刚刚入手新机准备要大玩一场的朋友来说，遇上这种事自然是非常苦恼。<br />\n<br />\n不过好在微软这边的反应还算及时，他们在了解情况后承诺会对问题主机进行更换，而且会免费提供一款 Mirosoft Studios 的 Xbox One 首发游戏供这些玩家下载。可选的作品包括有「Dead Rising 3」、「Forza Motorsport 5」、「Ryse: Son of Rome」或「Zoo Tycoon」，如果你也是不幸中标的玩家之一的话，先挑选一款聊以慰籍吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/25/xbox-one-hardware-problem-free-game/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.polygon.com/2013/11/25/5145620/xbox-one-owners-with-hardware-issues-get-complimentary-game\" target=\"_blank\">Polygon</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.wpcentral.com/microsoft-releases-statement-faulty-xbox-one-bluray-drives?utm_source=wpc&amp;utm_medium=twitter\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Phone Central</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/xbox-one-hardware-problem-free-game/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20776259/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/xbox-one-hardware-problem-free-game/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
